{"tid":392474,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"點解香港用呎","createTime":"2017-09-08T13:48:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-09T07:39:35.000Z","uid":14860,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"336b3989f254d50f19fd90e58bc7d7dd0a67647d","tid":392474,"uid":14860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T13:48:48.000Z","msg":"頭先食飯同人吹水 講開單位<br />\n講起香港有好多單位都用左公制單位<br />\n但點解賣屋賣樓都仲用緊呎呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f673e6ea9aa2b36157760a9caa921338f58712e2","tid":392474,"uid":137627,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T13:51:13.000Z","msg":"樓細用呎感覺良好，遲下用吋"},{"pid":"fb5aac19050c10f18556d05a055f1cc60cc4c703","tid":392474,"uid":21564,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T14:00:36.000Z","msg":"英尺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />完。"},{"pid":"8bc3bf9d8e5edb9d79639e0b95f5e8d09ffdb04c","tid":392474,"uid":51720,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T14:12:50.000Z","msg":"因為英治香港時期，必須跟宗主國嘅度量衡規定用英制。<br />\n即使上世紀80年代，港府推廣轉用公制（十進制），<br />\n但英制仍然係香港計算樓宇面積嘅度量衡標準。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d6265bf5043efc71820764188ee9a1a57e04b3a","tid":392474,"uid":90457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T07:39:35.000Z","msg":"三行度嘢都係用英制，因為真係易睇啲，公制啲mm眼花就會睇錯尺"}]}